Support

There are three ways that you can get support when using the Open Referral API--consider one of the following channels when you have a question, comment, or some feedback regarding the API and integration.

via Github via Twitter via Email

It is recommended that you start with submitting a Github issue, then maybe tweet at us. If your questions or comments require some privacy you should use email. Make sure you look through the existing issues before submitting a new one.
